<div id="siteNotice"><!-- CentralNotice --></div>
<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="de"><span dir="auto">Zilpzalp</span></h1>
<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
<div id="siteSub">aus Wikipedia, der freien Enzyklopädie</div>
<div id="contentSub">(Weitergeleitet von <a href="http://de.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Phylloscopus_collybita&amp;redirect=no" title="Phylloscopus collybita">Phylloscopus collybita</a>)<br />
</div>
<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
Wechseln zu: <a href="Phylloscopus_collybita#mw-navigation">Navigation</a>, <a href="Phylloscopus_collybita#p-search">Suche</a>
</div>
